title: [Anemone Villa, Woodsman's Study]
description: Warm sunlight spills through the windows to cast its warm, golden glow upon the large workbench that occupies the entire northern wall.  Ornately carved cupboards house various pieces of seasoned woods, while nearby shelves are lined with tools used for woodcarving.

Moonlight spills through the windows to cast its silvery glow upon the large workbench that occupies the entire northern wall.  Ornately carved cupboards house various pieces of seasoned woods, while nearby shelves are lined with tools used for woodcarving.
